subject: Fines (Penalties)
Football
lead_paragraph: An N.F.L. spokesman said plays from Week 12 looked at for potential discipline — like the one involving Detroit’s Ndamukong Suh and Green Bay’s Evan Dietrich-Smith — will not be reviewed until all games are completed.
